parties.feedbackmediator

Class FeedbackMediator

  • java.lang.Object
    • genius.core.parties.AbstractNegotiationParty
      • parties.feedbackmediator.FeedbackMediator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Mediator, NegotiationParty, java.io.Serializable

    public class FeedbackMediator
extends AbstractNegotiationParty
implements Mediator
    Implementation of a mediator that uses feedback to make a (partial) preference graph of the participating parties offers.

    This class was adapted from Reyhan's parties.SmartMediatorOnlyFeedback class (see svn history for details about that class), and adapted to fit into the new framework.

    Author:
    W.Pasman (compatibility fixes), David Festen, Reyhan (Orignal code)
    See Also:
